{"tid":2177169,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"Clifford Scott：相當證據顯示 721係港共黑警策劃既一場對民主運動既襲擊","createTime":"2020-08-27T13:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T17:25:17.000Z","uid":48083,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fe249ed599b956256d546cfd0e3912a0de7b1927","tid":2177169,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:54:59.000Z","msg":"1. It seems evident that the authorities in Hong Kong, including the HKPF, are aligning to produce a coordinated attack on the pro-democracy movement.<br />\n<br />\n2. We should perhaps not be surprised then, that this will revolve around a writing of their own history of 2019 in a manner that is in line with their ideological position of portraying the protest crowds as irrational mobs.<br />\n<br />\n3. The strategy involves a portrayal of these mobs being manipulated by criminal agitators, many of whom they argue are funded and influenced by antithetical external forces. On the basis of the evidence I have seen I would suggest that nothing could be further from the truth.<br />\n<br />\n4. Indeed, as crowd psychologists we have often seen the ways in which this form of crowd theory is used by political actors to deny the legitimate basis for protest, mask the role of state in the construction of crowd violence and to legitimise reactionary forms of policing.<br />\n<br />\n關於佢份報告：<br />\n<br />\nIt is in press with a journal and I hope will be published soon. Im afraid I don't know when this will be at this time.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/cliffordstott/status/1298873718723272705?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcliffordstott%2Fstatus%2F1298873718723272705%3Fs%3D21&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONpS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=e36c2fdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcliffordstott%2Fstatus%2F1298873718723272705%3Fs%3D21&h=6a6ee235\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/cliffordstott/status/1298873718723272705?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"589971f0a8c01511e45dd5135b50164a50125b08","tid":2177169,"uid":12586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37fd5db706c477c26bf7c12031527c06d90d4c20","tid":2177169,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:57:00.000Z","msg":"［廣傳］港共拒絕HKFP入境 上咗路透中國twitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2176827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2176827</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b539d7f5c838e0050ee6960845432359072873e2","tid":2177169,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bcc2f8d1e2183e407fac40b7cb8f798ed040906","tid":2177169,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:02:33.000Z","msg":"留名等睇佢份報告<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970fc7bd2e075ab0bba775435416981f241f6aa7","tid":2177169,"uid":24457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3151fd86fd3f3cdc518854368f8a8091d8b1d357","tid":2177169,"uid":49434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:03:05.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"48d383de51484cadd258704e5356c1912957b5b7","tid":2177169,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,